name: "First Love" Limited Edition Photos
description:
Special Limited Edition Photos

Your photo will be ONE of 10 in the WORLD.
       
"This is the REAL print"  that will grow in value.  Signed, Archival Silver Gelatin Print w/ COA.

Shipping of $24.95 within the United States and $64.95 for Intentional cost are for paper prints.

FRAMING: not included.  Average costs for special orders average cost for framing for simple black frames with black or white matt is $125.00 -$350 on up depending on size and frames. Once payment is cleared an invoice will be sent for addition shipping and handling and taxes where applicable.  

Thank you for your interest in Eriberto Oriol's original photos.

**These prices are exclusive to this site and not available when represented by gallery or consultant.  Check out other of Eriberto Oriol photos at MangoAzul.com and ForbiddenArtLA.com.
